          <h1 class="page-title">COC Management</h1>
          <p class="page-subtitle">Manage compensatory overtime credits</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body" style="text-align: center; padding: 4rem;">
            <i class="fas fa-business-time" style="font-size: 4rem; color: #e8ebed; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></i>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1f36; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">COC Management</h3>
            <p style="color: #697386;">Coming in Phase 2</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      `;
    }

    // ==================== REPORTS ====================
